Class FedmIscReaderInfo

java.lang.Object
  de.feig.FedmIscReaderInfo

public class FedmIscReaderInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Info class for the OBID i-scan® and OBID® classic-pro reader family.
This class collects all reader information.

rfcLicenseUhfTrType

public byte[] rfcLicenseUhfTrType
Device information from RF-Controller with [0x66] Reader Info and Mode=0x80.

Description:
Licensed transponder driver
Flag field with licensed UHF transponder types, if Reader is dual-frequency (HF and UHF) Reader.
If Reader is a single-frequency (UHR or HF) Reader, than transponder types are located in rfcLicenseTrType.
